data.description: This lovely 4/2.5/2 home is move-in ready.  Features include neutral colors throughout, 2-story entry, art niches, kitchen island, both formals, vaulted ceilings in the den, fabulous primary on 1st floor, his/her closets, jetted tub, and walk-in shower.   Upstairs game room, 3 bedrooms, bathroom, and plenty of storage.  Backyard access to a quiet park.  Marina is only a couple of blocks away.  No MUD Tax.
